<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>والطبراني في <span class="c1">"الأوسط"</span> <span class="c2">(١٣٩٤)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
